item.title: Can someone help me with Welcome to Runescape at the start when u logg in
item.dc:creator: @WonkeyWoo WonkeyWoo
item.description:
@WonkeyWoo wrote:

You need to look for the following in your client.

sendMessage("Welcome to Runescape.");

Then change that to.

sendMessage("Welcome to Timscape.");
